judicialResults.label: Youth rehabilitation order with fostering England / Wales
judicialResults.resultText:
YROFEW - Youth rehabilitation order with fostering England / Wales
Youth rehabilitation order with fostering made. The defendant must comply with the requirements (shown below) by 05/03/2025 commencing on 06/03/2023. Live for 12 Months with a Wandsworth Borough Council foster parent. Judge reserves breach proceedings.

judicialResults.label: Youth rehabilitation requirement: Drug treatment as a non-resident
judicialResults.resultText:
YRD2 - Youth rehabilitation requirement: Drug treatment as a non-resident
Youth rehabilitation requirement: Drug treatment requirement. To submit to treatment as a non-resident at PlaceX for 6 Months by or under the direction of PersonX with a view to the reduction or elimination of your dependency on or propensity to misuse drugs.
